query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS health_checks (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  check_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  check_type ENUM('database', 'api_endpoint', 'external_service', 'resource_usage', 'custom') NOT NULL,
  check_config JSON NOT NULL,
  schedule_type ENUM('minute', 'hourly', 'daily', 'custom') NOT NULL,
  schedule_interval INT DEFAULT 5,
  cron_expression VARCHAR(100),
  warning_threshold INT,
  critical_threshold INT,
  is_active BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT TRUE,
  last_check_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  next_check_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  current_status ENUM('healthy', 'warning', 'critical', 'unknown') DEFAULT 'unknown',
  created_by INT NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
